---
// Alianzas.astro
---

<section class="alianzas">
  <div class="alianzas-container">
    <div class="heading-column">
      <h3 class="heading-white">El poder de</h3>
      <h2 class="heading-yellow">las alianzas</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="content-column">
      <div class="text-content">
        <p class="body-text">
          La colaboración es la base para crear soluciones excepcionales. Junto a socios estratégicos como <strong>Ancient Technologies, Ideograma y TopDesign</strong>, unimos nuestra experiencia para desarrollar proyectos únicos. Esta sinergia impulsa la innovación, nos mantiene a la vanguardia y expande los límites del diseño y el desarrollo.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="logos-container">
        <img 
          src="https://pub-d17bbbdbf8e348c5a57c8168ad69c92f.r2.dev/AncientGreen.svg" 
          alt="Ancient Technologies"
          class="partner-logo"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <img 
          src="https://pub-d17bbbdbf8e348c5a57c8168ad69c92f.r2.dev/IdeogramaGreen.svg" 
          alt="Ideograma"
          class="partner-logo"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <img 
          src="https://pub-d17bbbdbf8e348c5a57c8168ad69c92f.r2.dev/TopDesignGreen.svg" 
          alt="TopDesign"
          class="partner-logo"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .alianzas {
    margin: 200px 0px;
    padding: 200px 100px;
    background: var(--color-black-b);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .alianzas-container {
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: flex-start;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 100px;
  }

  .heading-column {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: flex-start;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 14px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .heading-white {
    color: var(--color-white);
    font-size: var(--heading-4-size);
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: var(--heading-4-line-height);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .heading-yellow {
    color: var(--color-yellow);
    font-size: var(--heading-1-size);
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: var(--heading-1-line-height);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .content-column {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: flex-start;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 60px;
    padding: 20px 100px 20px 0;
  }

  .text-content {
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .body-text {
    color: var(--color-white);
    font-size: var(--body-1-size);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: var(--body-1-line-height);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .body-text strong {
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .logos-container {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: flex-start;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 60px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .partner-logo {
    height: 32px;
    width: auto;
    object-fit: contain;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, opacity 0.3s ease;
  }

  .partner-logo:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  /* Responsive Design */
  @media (max-width: 1400px) {
    .alianzas {
      padding: 80px 50px;
    }

    .alianzas-container {
      gap: 60px;
    }

    .content-column {
      padding-right: 0;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .alianzas {
      padding: 60px 40px;
    }

    .alianzas-container {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 40px;
    }

    .heading-column {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .content-column {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 0;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .alianzas {
      padding: 40px 30px;
    }

    .heading-white {
      font-size: var(--heading-5-size);
      line-height: var(--heading-5-line-height);
    }

    .heading-yellow {
      font-size: var(--heading-2-size);
      line-height: var(--heading-2-line-height);
    }

    .logos-container {
      gap: 40px;
    }

    .partner-logo {
      height: 24px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .alianzas {
      padding: 30px 20px;
    }

    .heading-white {
      font-size: 24px;
      line-height: 28px;
    }

    .heading-yellow {
      font-size: 36px;
      line-height: 40px;
    }

    .content-column {
      gap: 40px;
    }

    .body-text {
      font-size: var(--body-2-size);
    }

    .logos-container {
      gap: 30px;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .partner-logo {
      height: 20px;
    }
  }
</style>
